text: Daniuska Carrasco (born 7 August 1997) is a Cuban water polo player. She was a member of the Cuba women's national water polo team at the 2019 Pan American Games and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Others websites == * daniuska-carrasco-leyva * cuban-players-daniuska-carrasco-and- arisel-gonzalez * 18th-fina-world-aquatics-championships Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban water polo players
